Package asgn1Election

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Collection
    Interface to specify a collection of asgn1Election.Vote objects and the operations permissible.
    Vote
    Interface to specify a collection of Integers representing a vote.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Candidate
    Class defines information about a single candidate in an election: the name, full party name, party acronym and the number of votes received.
    CandidateIndex
    Simple class to provide an Integer representation of the index of a candidate in an election, and to restrict it to a sensible range.
    Election
    Abstract class to specify the workings of a seat based election.
    ElectionManager
    Class to run a seat based election.
    PrefElection
    Subclass of Election, specialised to preferential, but not optional preferential voting.
    SimpleElection
    Subclass of Election, specialised to simple, first past the post voting
    VoteCollection
    Class to manage a collection of Votes as specified by the Collection interface.
    VoteList
    Implementing class for the Vote interface.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ElectionException
    This class represents exceptions associated with Election and associated classes.
